<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10947] Allow subclassing of HTable and HBaseAdmin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10947</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To extend functionality of HTable and HBaseAdmin we may need to subclass them. This JIRA allows to add a default constructor and probably remove the final variables in them so that we could subclass them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12707507">HBASE-10947</key>
            <summary>Allow subclassing of HTable and HBaseAdmin</summary>
